text: Volha Berazniova (born 10 May 1980 in Minsk, Belarus) is a Belarusian rower. She competed in the women's eight at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the women's quadruple sculls at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belarus Category:Rowers at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk Category:1980 births Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
